page_title: "Set up Advanced Network Observability for Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS) - BYO Prometheus and Grafana"

chunk_content:
Clean up resources

If you don't plan on using this application, delete the other resources you created in this article using the `az group delete` command.

```azurecli-interactive
  az group delete --name $RESOURCE_GROUP
```
